’Щ@8ff5c11539449b8c426eab9efc864adb554e1a56f22dfecb6d1b1eff0aa70f60Ъ%Title: title: version check
Path: Notes
Content:
If you're running nushell nightly, 
``version check``
 will check to see if you are running the latest nightly version. If you are running the nushell release, 
``version check``
 will check to see if you're running the latest release version.
